WEBVTT

00:00:58.395 --> 00:01:00.995
CA: And the quest for renewable energy.

00:01:01.315 --> 00:01:04.656
(TED Talk) BG: We need solutions,
either one or several,

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:07.783
that have unbelievable scale

00:01:07.807 --> 00:01:09.741
and unbelievable reliability.

00:01:10.220 --> 00:01:13.641
And although there's many directions
that people are seeking,

00:01:13.665 --> 00:01:17.427
I really only see five
that can achieve the big numbers.

00:01:17.451 --> 00:01:20.480
(Music)

00:01:20.504 --> 00:01:22.345
CA: Bill is a knowledge sponge,

00:01:22.369 --> 00:01:24.734
and is passionate about so many things.

00:01:24.758 --> 00:01:27.512
We talked about the current
state of technology

00:01:27.536 --> 00:01:32.827
and about a man facing the same kind
of scrutiny he was 20 years ago,